      <h2> Linux users </h2>
      <p>
        KompoZer is a GTK application, it has nothing to do with KDE — though it can be installed on KDE, too. Komodo and the Kernel aren’t KDE applications either. ;-)
      </p>
      <p>
        KompoZer 0.7.10 is not compatible with GTK ≥ 2.14, hence the crashes on some recent Linux distros like Ubuntu 8.10 and 9.04.
        Please upgrade to <a href="/download.php">KompoZer 0.8</a>.
      </p>

      <h2> Contribute! </h2>
      <p>
        Developers, translators, testers: please visit <a href="http://kompozer.sourceforge.net/">kompozer.sf.net</a> if you want to contribute to this project.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you like KompoZer, please consider <a href="/donate.php">making a donation</a> to support this project.
        The current development needs your donations to keep going!
      </p>
